metadata.description: Relationship 'summary' and all reports and report views.

configuration.name: description
configuration.value: Total number of facilities in the district, division or state.

configuration.name: qry
configuration.value: CASE WHEN NULLIF(`district+id`,'') IS NOT NULL THEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM hippo_facility WHERE location = `district+id` OR location IN (SELECT id FROM hippo_county WHERE district = `district+id`)) WHEN NULLIF(`division+id`,'') IS NOT NULL THEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM hippo_facility WHERE location = `division+id`) WHEN NULLIF(`state+id`,'') IS NOT NULL THEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM hippo_facility WHERE location = `state+id`) ELSE 0 END

configuration.name: qry
configuration.value: CASE WHEN NULLIF(`mbbs+id`,'') IS NOT NULL AND NULLIF(`specialist+id`,'') IS NOT NULL THEN 'Specialist' WHEN NULLIF(`mbbs+id`,'') IS NOT NULL THEN 'General Doctor' WHEN NULLIF(`dental+id`,'') IS NOT NULL THEN 'Dental' WHEN NULLIF(`ayush+id`,'') IS NOT NULL THEN 'AYUSH' WHEN NULLIF(`anm+id`,'') IS NOT NULL THEN 'ANM' WHEN NULLIF(`nurse+id`,'') IS NOT NULL THEN 'Nurse' ELSE 'Other Health Staff' END
